  "description": "From the manufacturer ABOUT CARPLAN DEMON Demon – Try it, you’ll love it! CarPlan Demon Range covers everything you would possibly need to fully valet your car from roof to tires. Our colorful range of products is made for simplicity and results that will leave a lasting impression as well as wonderful fragrances. More than that, Demon’s universal formulations are not just for cars. From Bikes, Quads, RVs, and Caravans, to Tractors and Boats, Demon Shines it ALL! CarPlan Demon brings the fun back into cleaning your vehicle. You don't need fancy pressure washers, expensive waxes and polishing machines to get a showroom finish. Just let the Demon do the work! The technologically advanced and innovative formulations are designed to tackle every aspect of cleaning a vehicle whether it be interior or exterior and give you exceptional results every single time. Our patented Venturi Foam and Shine Guns simply connect to your garden hose and off you go!",
